# Agent Field Kit

This Claude environment is managed by Agent Field Kit for `${profile_name}`.

## Server Ports

Use `${portbroker_command}` before launching any local server. Do not choose a
port by convention.

```sh
PORT=$(${portbroker_command} get --name <service> 2>/dev/null || ${portbroker_command} alloc --name <service> --host ${default_host} --persistent)
```

Bind to `${default_host}` unless the user asks for localhost-only behavior.

Every new HTTP service should implement:

```text
GET /whoami
```

The endpoint should return service name, version, pid, start time, host, and
port.

## Writing Checks

Use `${prose_hygiene_command}` when the user asks to scrub prose or remove em
dashes.

## Publishing Checks

Before GitHub publishing:

```sh
${github_command} auth status
```

Before Apps Script publishing:

```sh
${clasp_command} ${clasp_auth_check_command}
test -f .clasp.json
```

